					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-462616#post-1422375</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-462616/scp-1209#post-1422375</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 20 Apr 2012 15:39:19 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Rioghail</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1302192</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>After failing twice to complete Bright's 24-hour challenge, I finally manage to make one in 2 hours and he downvotes it. Such is life, I guess.</p> <p>The image has definitely appeared on the wiki before, in <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/document-8668206-dg">Document 8668206 Dg</a>, and if someone else made a main-list article for it before me they should have removed it from that list. I've always wanted to write an article for one of the images on that list, and I finally had a decent idea for one, so I decided to go for it.</p> <p>Thanks for all the feedback. I've gone back through and fixed some of the errors that people have pointed out, and explained the lack of amnesiac use.</p> <p>And, of course, mad props to Gears for compiling the images document I found the original image in, and to Raven Mackenzie for adding the tags to this article after I forgot to.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
